
@{
    Layout = null;
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>About Us</title>

    <link href="~/css/about.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">

    <!-- Latest compiled and minified CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">

    <!-- jQuery library -->
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.4.1/jquery.min.js"></script>

    <!-- Popper JS -->
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css"></script>

    <!-- Latest compiled JavaScript -->
    <script src="~/js/caroufredsel.js" type="text/javascript"></script>

    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

</head>

<body>

    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <img src="~/images/yellowlogo.png" alt="Alternate Text" class="logo" />
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a asp-action="Index" asp-controller="Home">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a asp-action="About" asp-controller="Home">About</a></li>
                    <li><a asp-action="Contact" asp-controller="Home">Contact</a></li>
                    <li><a asp-action="App" asp-controller="Home">Mobile App</a></li>
                    <li><a asp-action="Login" asp-controller="Users">Admin</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="intro-area white" id="intro">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-12 text-center">
                    <h2>Helping You Plan for Success</h2>
                    <div class="sub-heading">
                        <p>
                            Goal Pro Solutions is a platform for all young people to take ownership <br>
                            of their futures through goal setting and planning for success in their lives

                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-4">

                    <div class="intro-block">
                        <span class="intro-icon"><i class="fa fa-id-card"></i></span>
                        <h3>ABOUT US</h3>
                        <p>
                            We aim to create a safe place that brings freedom,
                            life and growth to our youth.
                            We achieve this by providing and creating a platform that will bring motivation,
                            encouragement and tools needed to recognize their unique gifts, talents and differences.
                            We align ourselves with both the public and private institutions and offer an amazing opportunity for brand awareness and involvement.

                        </p>

                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4">

                    <div class="intro-block">
                        <span class="intro-icon"><i class="fa fa-heart"></i></span>
                        <h3>OUR HEART</h3>
                        <p>
                            Our heart is to see every one of our youth have a vision for their lives,
                            to help them realize there is so much potential and gifting in each young person.
                            We believe in an ideal that everyone is born with a purpose to live out,
                            and we believe it is our duty to walk alongside and assist them in realizing their potential, passions and gifts.

                        </p>

                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-sm-4">

                    <div class="intro-block">
                        <span class="intro-icon"><i class="fa fa-star"></i></span>
                        <h3>WHAT WE BELIEVE IN</h3>
                        <p>
                            •	We believe in raising strong, self-aware and confident young people who can lead themselves and those around them well.<br>
                            •	We believe in celebrating uniqueness and difference.<br>
                            •	We believe in supporting entrepreneurship to help curb unemployment.<br>
                            •	We believe in the future of our youth-our amazing generation.<br>
                            •	We believe that our youth are our greatest assets.<br>


                        </p>

                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-sm-4">

                    <div class="intro-block center">
                        <span class="intro-icon"><i class="fa fa-list-alt"></i></span>
                        <h3>OUR OBJECTIVES</h3>
                        <p>
                            •	When we equip one young person with Hope and Encouragement, we have given a breath of life to their dreams despite their circumstances.<br>
                            •	We aspire to keep our youth in school to complete their matric and to set goals beyond what they can imagine.<br>
                            •	We want our youth to see in themselves what we know they already have and what the world needs.<br>
                            •	Life is a gift and we are here to help each young person live their best life possible and to show them there is a plan for them.

                        </p>

                    </div>
                </div>


            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section></section>
</body>
</html>